Table and plot of monthly means (2014-2022) - EOL temperature & salinity
monthly_means <- ungroup(EOL_RAW) %>% 
  mutate(Month = format(datetime, format="%m")) %>% 
  group_by(Month) %>%
  summarise(
    Salinity_month = mean(salinity, na.rm = TRUE),
    SD_sal = sd(salinity, na.rm = TRUE),
    Temperature_month = mean(temperature, na.rm = TRUE),
    SD_temp = sd(temperature, na.rm = TRUE),
    Oxy_month = mean(oxygen, na.rm = TRUE),
    SD_oxy = sd(oxygen, na.rm= TRUE))


##RAPPORT##

monthly_means_rapport <- monthly_means %>% 
  mutate(`T (Â°C)` = paste(round(Temperature_month, digits=2), "Â±", round(SD_temp, digits=2)),

         `O~2~ (Âµmol.kg^-1^)` = paste(round(Oxy_month, digits=2), "Â±", round(SD_oxy, digits=2)))
